                                <span class="help-tip" tabindex="0">?<span class="tip-content">If the PARITY Act ($200/transaction) or Lummis bill ($300/transaction with $5K annual cap) is enacted, much of the tax-event load on small everyday bitcoin spending evaporates. Toggle this on to see the LoB scenario without the tax friction.</span></span>
                            </span>
